name: Leonard Whitney
text: Average D'Angelo chain restaurant. Good selection of sandwiches and other food such as soup and grain bowls. Parking is free and building is easy to see from street. Delivery is offered as is online ordering. They also have a rewards ‚Ä¶More

name: Regina Wessling
text: Visiting here from out of state and stopped here Thursday and had an awesome sandwhich. A couple of guys grilling the sandwhiches.  Here again on a Saturday afternoon, 2 young girls behind the grill. Terrible, nothing like the one the other day. Won't be back. I got it to go or would've complained there.

text: Subs are good, but the only people actually working are the shift supervisors.
